This is a repo containing a presentation about Linux and the recent
spate of Spectre issues.  Originally given at LinuxCon Japan and China
in June 2018.  Updated in August 2018 for OSS North America 2018.

Also in here is a presentation for 2019 about MDS and other Spectre-like
issues that have recently happened.  Presented in China in June 2019,
Japan July 2019, and OSS North America in August 2019.

Please see the file, additional_resources.txt for lots of good backup
material to learn all about these issues.

